title: Chicago 18 (XVIII)
description:
The last of David Foster as producer, the first with Jason Scheff who has now spent 20 years with the band so it&#039;s as much his as it was Pete&#039;s, I figure.  Humberto Gatica won a Grammy for this.  Not sure why, apparently it was really really good engineering.

Niagara Falls

Forever

If She Would Have Been Faithful

25 or 6 ro 4

Will You Still Love Me?

Over and Over
